---
title: Summer Turkey Pesto Pasta with Basil and Zucchini
description: We've put a big summer twist on the classic Bolognese by swapping in turkey and pesto and adding zucchini. Together, these ingredients create an incredible depth of flavour to make a delicious sunny day pasta!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pates-estivales-a-la-dinde-et-au-pesto-c8a58623.jpg
